 font-size:9pt">.  Finally I wish to suggest </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.6pt; text-indent:-21.6pt"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">1.3.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">Design approaches</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">, which could be of considerable benefit and at little effective cost to enable a greater take-up of the bicycle as a means of transport</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> (§5)</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="2" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 13.54pt; padding-left:4.46pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline">Q1: Is cycling </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline">is safe, particularly in towns and cities?</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 39.6pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">2.1.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">Generally cycling is </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">convenient and </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">safe, </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">as reported by many others,</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> but </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">a range of barriers affects a person’s choice of a bicycle for utilitarian travel purposes.</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> This is</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">reported</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> in the Policy implications </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">from the EPSRC “</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">Understanding Walking and Cycling</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">” Project</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> (UW&amp;C)</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> 2008 - 2011:</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><a href="http://www.lec.lancs.ac.uk/research/society_and_environment/walking_and_cycling.php"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:7pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.lec.lancs.ac.uk/research/society_and_environment/walking_and_cycling.</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:7pt; text-decoration:underline">php</span></a><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">which </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">I endorse, it </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">concludes:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 61.2pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-25.2pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold">2.1.1.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold">Policy Implications</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 28.35pt 0pt 61.2pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-25.2pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">2.1.2.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">The key message</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> that</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">… </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">cycling</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">[is] </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">perceived to take too much effort, need planning and equipment that</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">causes hassle, and may be risky and uncomfortable. </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">[cyclists]</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline"> also run the risk of being perceived</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">by others as eccentric or odd</span><span style="font-family:'L