ly:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">…</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 61.5pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-18.95pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">…</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> there need to be effective </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">restrictions on traffic speeds, parking and access on all</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">residential roads and other routes without segregated cycle and pedestrian paths</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">…</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 61.5pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-18.95pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">…</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> the system of legal liability on roads used by the public should be changed to</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">protect the most vulnerable road users (cyclists and pedestrians). </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> …</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 61.5pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-18.95pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">… it is necessary </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; text-decoration:underline">to change the image of cycling</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">..</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">. To a great extent</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">this should be consequential on the</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> above changes: as more people walk and cycle then</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">more people will accept it as normal. </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">…</span></p><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 13.54pt; orphans:0; padding-left:4.46pt; text-indent:0pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">Prior to t</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">he extensive UW&amp;C research</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">I began </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">exploration</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">into</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">perceptions</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> of risk</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">in the </span><span style="font-family:'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-size:9pt">19</span><span style="font-family:'Lucida San